      <li>
        <a class="app-contact-panel__link" href="https://github.com/nhsuk/nhsuk-service-manual/blob/redesign/nav/app/views/design-system/{{pageSection|lower}}/{{pageTitle|lower|replace(" ", "-")}}.njk">propose a change to this page</a> - read more about <a class="app-contact-panel__link" href="/community/propose-a-content-change-using-github/">how to propose changes in GitHub</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  {% else %}
      <p>
        If you spot a problem with the {{pageTitle}} guidance you can <a class="app-contact-panel__link" href="https://github.com/nhsuk/nhsuk-service-manual/blob/redesign/nav/app/views/design-system/{{pageSection|lower}}/{{pageTitle|lower|replace(" ", "-")}}.njk">propose a change</a>.
        </p>
        <p>If you're not sure how to do this, read guidance on <a class="app-contact-panel__link" href="/service-manual/community/propose-a-content-change-using-github/">how to propose changes in GitHub</a>.
      </p>
  {% endif %}
{% endif %}

